      "content": `AI image generation has exploded in 2026. Whether you need photorealistic portraits, marketing graphics, or logo designs, there's an AI image generator for every need.\n\nHere are our top 10 picks.\n\n## 1. Midjourney\n\nProduces the highest quality AI-generated images in the industry. Its artistic style and attention to detail consistently outperform competitors.\n\n**Best for:** Visual creators and designers\n**Price:** Paid plans from $10/month\n\n## 2. DALL-E 3\n\nBuilt into ChatGPT for the easiest AI image generation experience. Natural language conversation makes it accessible to everyone.\n\n**Best for:** ChatGPT users and marketers\n**Price:** Included with ChatGPT Plus ($20/month)\n\n## 3. Stable Diffusion\n\nOpen-source and completely free if run locally. Total control over generation with an enormous ecosystem of community models.\n\n**Best for:** Tech-savvy users and privacy-focused creators\n**Price:** Free (local), paid hosting available\n\n## 4. Canva AI (Magic Studio)\n\nIncredibly easy to use with a massive template library. Perfect for non-designers who need professional-quality graphics.\n\n**Best for:** Non-designers and marketers\n**Price:** Free tier available, Pro $12.99/month\n\n## 5. Adobe Firefly\n\nTrained on Adobe Stock for commercial-safe AI image generation. Integrates directly into Photoshop and Illustrator.\n\n**Best for:** Creative Cloud users\n**Price:** Free tier available, included with Creative Cloud\n\n## 6. Ideogram\n\nSpecializes in text-in-image rendering — the best tool for creating graphics with accurate typography.\n\n**Best for:** Designers needing text in images\n**Price:** Free tier available\n\n## 7. Leonardo AI\n\nGreat free tier with fine-tuned models for game assets, illustrations, and digital art.\n\n**Best for:** Game devs and illustrators\n**Price:** Free tier available\n\n## 8. Recraft\n\nGenerates scalable vector graphics (SVG) — unique among AI image generators. Essential for logo designers and icon creators.\n\n**Best for:** Logo designers and icon creators\n**Price:** Free tier available\n\n## 9. PhotoRoom\n\nExcellent background removal and product photo enhancement. A must-have for e-commerce sellers.\n\n**Best for:** E-commerce sellers and photographers\n**Price:** Free tier available\n\n## 10. Kittl\n\nGreat for merch design with excellent templates and AI text effects. Popular among Print-on-Demand entrepreneurs.\n\n**Best for:** Merch designers and POD sellers\n**Price:** Free tier available`
