deal for corporate training.\n\n**Best for:** Corporate training and educators\n**Price:** Paid plans from $22/month\n\n## 10. Vizard\n\nConverts long videos into short clips with automatic captioning and platform optimization.\n\n**Best for:** YouTubers and podcasters\n**Price:** Free tier available`
